description: Now monthly! Zatanna’s father Zatara has gone missing! With the Justice League off on a mission, it’s up to Scooby and the gang to unravel the magical mystery by joining Zatanna to blaze a trail through the spookiest corners of the DC Universe.
name: Scooby-Doo and the Conjuror's Conundrum

description: A group of friends who are young soccer fans, dream of one day becoming as good as their champions and integrate the PSG Academy, the school for the PSG stars of tomorrow in the saint of all saints, the Parc des Princes. Through their efforts and their exploits, they will be accompanied by real players, coaches for a day but also big brothers and protectors. In the eyes of the kids, these players are true superheroes!
name: Rivalités

description: Will Tom and his friends, (with the help of Maxwell, Zlatan, Cavani and Silva) manage to beat the Munich Academy?
name: Affrontements

description: A match ! A final match to win and PSG Academy will participate in the final stage of the great tournament. But for that, they will have to defeat a very motivated opponent!
name: Gagner ensemble

description: They had succeeded! PSG Academy is qualified for the final tournament involving the best teams in Europe.
name: En route vers la finale
